.000Z","msg":"Sor, 平時蒙頭入閘"},{"pid":"8d6485f9f17e1092aa0211fb394c2c2be08788ca","tid":739963,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:31:36.000Z","msg":"倫敦金呃足幾廿年都無事，今次呃左個大陸人即刻比人剷起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a49b680bf24298abd49d2a3102bd56732b2385b","tid":739963,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d6485f9f17e1092aa0211fb394c2c2be08788ca","tid":739963,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:31:36.000Z","msg":"倫敦金呃足幾廿年都無事，今次呃左個大陸人即刻比人剷起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:33:16.000Z","msg":"係咪呃左d大粒佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}